eritage. Not willing to be marginalized, descendants of the New Paltz Walloons constructed an alternative national narrative, placing their ancestors at the very center of the American story.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 4aHistory : History. 4aNew York/Regional : New York/Regional. 7aHISTORY / United States / State & Local / Middle Atlantic (DC, DE, MD, NJ, NY, PA).2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143846437440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438464374423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438464374/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles